<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Won Tech Blog]]></title><description><![CDATA[Blog posted about ...]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 06:09:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[React에서 UseRef란?]]></title><description><![CDATA[UseRef란 공식문서에서 는 “a React Hook that reference a value that’s not needed for rendering…]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com/React/useref/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com/React/useref/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:12:25 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h3 id=&quot;useref란&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#useref%EB%9E%80&quot; aria-label=&quot;useref란 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;UseRef란&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;공식문서에서 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;useRef&lt;/code&gt;는 “a React Hook that reference a value that’s not needed for rendering”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;“렌더링에 필요하지 않은 값 참조할 수 있게 해주는 리액트 훅”&lt;/strong&gt;이라고 정의되어 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; ref &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;useRef&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;initialValue&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
console&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;ref&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;// { current: initalValue }&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;useRef&lt;/code&gt;는 항상 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;{object}&lt;/code&gt;의 값을 리턴하고, 안에는 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;.current&lt;/code&gt; 프로퍼티에 저장합니다. 저장하는 값은 모두 이곳에 담깁니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;초기값인 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;initialValue&lt;/code&gt;를 넣을 수 있고, 첫 렌더링에만 값이 적용되며, 다음 렌더링에는 값이 적용되지 않습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;dom-노드-저장-및-내장-메소드를-사용할-수-있다&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#dom-%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5-%EB%B0%8F-%EB%82%B4%EC%9E%A5-%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8B%A4&quot; aria-label=&quot;dom 노드 저장 및 내장 메소드를 사용할 수 있다 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;DOM 노드 저장 및 내장 메소드를 사용할 수 있다.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; nodeRef &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;useRef&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token class-name&quot;&gt;View&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token attr-name&quot;&gt;ref&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token script language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token script-punctuation punctuation&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;nodeRef&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;typescript에서-useref란&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#typescript%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-useref%EB%9E%80&quot; aria-label=&quot;typescript에서 useref란 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;TypeScript에서 useRef란?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;tsx&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-tsx&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-tsx&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token class-name&quot;&gt;RefObject&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token constant&quot;&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;readonly&lt;/span&gt; current&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token constant&quot;&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token class-name&quot;&gt;MutableRefObject&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token constant&quot;&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  current&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token constant&quot;&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RefObject의 정의를 보면 초기값을 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;.current&lt;/code&gt;에 저장합니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; localVarRef &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; useRef &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; number &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;로컬 변수 용도로 사용할 경우 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;MutableRefObject&amp;lt;T&gt;&lt;/code&gt; 제네릭 타입과 같은 타입의 초깃값을 넣어줍니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; inputRef &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; useRef &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; HTMLInputElement &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DOM을 직접 조작하기 위해 사용할 경우 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;RefObject&amp;lt;T&gt;&lt;/code&gt; 초깃값으로 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;을 넣어줍니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;references&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#references&quot; aria-label=&quot;references permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;References&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef&quot;&gt;https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
